						</div>
					</div>

					<section class="content-section">
						<h2>The Challenge: A Field in Crisis</h2>
						<div class="section-content">
							<div class="challenge-overview">
								<p>By 2023, Westlake Academy's once-pristine artificial turf field had deteriorated significantly. What started as minor cosmetic issues had evolved into serious safety and performance concerns that threatened the school's athletic programs.</p>
							</div>

							<div class="problems-grid">
								<div class="problem-item severe">
									<h3>GMAX Safety Failure</h3>
									<div class="metric">
										<span class="value">235g</span>
										<span class="label">Average GMAX reading</span>
									</div>
									<p>Multiple field areas tested above 200g, with some spots exceeding 250g - well beyond safe limits for student athletes.</p>
								</div>

								<div class="problem-item high">
									<h3>Severe Compaction</h3>
									<div class="metric">
										<span class="value">40%</span>
										<span class="label">Infill loss in goal areas</span>
									</div>
									<p>Goal areas and high-traffic zones had lost significant infill, creating hard, potentially dangerous playing surfaces.</p>
								</div>

								<div class="problem-item moderate">
									<h3>Drainage Issues</h3>
									<div class="metric">
										<span class="value">6+ hours</span>
										<span class="label">Standing water after rain</span>
									</div>
									<p>Poor drainage led to game cancellations and limited field availability, disrupting the athletic program schedule.</p>
								</div>

								<div class="problem-item high">
									<h3>Fiber Deterioration</h3>
									<div class="metric">
										<span class="value">60%</span>
										<span class="label">Fiber matting in center field</span>
									</div>
									<p>Matted and worn fibers created inconsistent playing surfaces and increased injury risk for cutting movements.</p>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="crisis-quote">
								<blockquote>
									<p>"We were facing a choice between shutting down our home field or risking serious student injuries. The field had become a liability we couldn't ignore."</p>
								</blockquote>
								<cite>Mike Thompson, Athletic Director<br>Westlake Academy</cite>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<section class="content-section">
						<h2>The Decision: Restore vs. Replace</h2>
