								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="decision-factors">
								<h3>Key Decision Factors</h3>
								<ul>
									<li><strong>Budget constraints:</strong> $73,500 vs. $1,005,000 - a 93% cost savings</li>
									<li><strong>Minimal disruption:</strong> Work completed during summer break</li>
									<li><strong>Proven track record:</strong> Similar successful restorations at other schools</li>
									<li><strong>Extended field life:</strong> Professional assessment showed 8+ more years possible</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<section class="content-section">
						<h2>The Solution: Comprehensive Field Restoration</h2>
						<div class="section-content">
							<div class="solution-timeline">
								<div class="phase-item">
									<div class="phase-number">1</div>
									<div class="phase-content">
										<h3>Assessment & Planning</h3>
										<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 1 week</p>
										<ul>
											<li>Comprehensive GMAX testing across 50+ field locations</li>
											<li>Infill depth measurements and distribution analysis</li>
											<li>Drainage system evaluation and flow testing</li>
											<li>Fiber condition assessment and wear pattern mapping</li>
											<li>Custom restoration plan development</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="phase-item">
									<div class="phase-number">2</div>
									<div class="phase-content">
										<h3>Deep Cleaning & Preparation</h3>
										<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 1.5 weeks</p>
										<ul>
											<li>Industrial-grade deep cleaning to remove organic debris</li>
											<li>Antimicrobial treatment for bacteria and odor elimination</li>
											<li>Drainage system clearing and flow restoration</li>
											<li>Fiber extraction and cleaning in heavily matted areas</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="phase-item">
									<div class="phase-number">3</div>
									<div class="phase-content">
										<h3>Structural Restoration</h3>
										<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 2 weeks</p>
										<ul>
											<li>Infill removal, cleaning, and redistribution</li>
											<li>Addition of 40 tons of new premium infill material</li>
											<li>Precision leveling and compaction adjustment</li>
											<li>Fiber restoration and vertical alignment</li>
											<li>Seam inspection and reinforcement</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="phase-item">
									<div class="phase-number">4</div>
									<div class="phase-content">
										<h3>Quality Assurance & Testing</h3>
										<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 1.5 weeks</p>
