											<li>Post-restoration GMAX testing verification</li>
											<li>Drainage performance testing</li>
											<li>Playing surface consistency evaluation</li>
											<li>Line marking and field preparation</li>
											<li>Final safety inspection and certification</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
