						<h2>Lessons Learned & Best Practices</h2>
						<div class="section-content">
							<div class="lessons-grid">
								<div class="lesson-item">
									<h3>Early Intervention Pays</h3>
									<p>Addressing field issues at the first signs of deterioration costs significantly less than waiting until conditions become severe.</p>
